[normal]5.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]The issue of holding Chief Constables to account is considered under the second specific item of your review, but it is important to note the success of PCCs in the first two tests that are set out above, namely on 
[normal]visibility[bold] and on 
[normal]driving innovation[bold].
