[normal]Visibility[bold]&#xa0;[bold]6.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]PCCs have brought openness and transparency to their scrutiny role, in contrast to the invisible and unaccountable police authorities.  In Avon and Somerset, the PCC and the C
[normal]hief 
[normal]C
[normal]onstable
