[normal]7.
[normal]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]It is clear that this approach is bearing fruit.  Only seven per cent of people knew that they could go to their police authorities with concerns about policing and crime in their area.  
[normal]In contrast, 7 in 10 people know about police and crime commissioner
[normal]s
[normal].
