[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]10.
[normal] 
[normal]In Kent, the PCC has rolled out a fleet of ‘Mobile Police Contact Points’ that will make 360 visits to 180 locations in the county each month.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] This allows members of the public in rural areas to report a crime or anti-social behaviour
[normal];
[normal] meet their local PCSOs
[normal],
[normal] 
[normal]and discuss any local policing issues or concerns they have.
